videos.description: After hustle defense forces the turnover, Isaiah Briscoe feeds a streaking Edrice Adebayo, who throws down the vicious two-handed slam for the hoop and the harm in Kentucky's game against Arizona State in the Bahamas.
videos.headline: Adebayo rattling the Bahamas with a vicious dunk and-1

videos.description: Malik Monk made Three Point Jumper from the corner as Kentucky takes a 36-18 lead
videos.headline: Wildcats keep rolling after Monk 3

videos.description: Malik Monk makes crazy layup for a 42-25 lead
videos.headline: Monk goes dipsy-do for 2

videos.description: ASU Kodi Justice drains the deep 3 from the wing
videos.headline: K. Justice trying to keep ASU alive with deep 3

videos.description: De'Aaron Fox made Three Point Jumper as Kentucky takes 58-30 lead into halftime
videos.headline: Kentucky ends impressive 1st half with a Fox 3

videos.description: Kentucky is flying against Arizona State, especially when Isaiah Briscoe throws the full-court perfect pass to a streaking Derek Willis, who makes the catch and the dunk for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Kentucky goes end to end for dunk without needing a dribble

videos.description: Kentucky is showing why they're the top-ranked team when Malik Monk makes one of the assists of the year, diving out of bounds but still making the one-handed assist to Wenyen Gabriel for the huge reverse slam.
videos.headline: Assist of the year candidate leads to awesome reverse dunk

videos.description: Brad Calipari hits the corner 3 as Wildcats go up 104-63
videos.headline: Calipari chips in with 3 pointer

videos.description: Dan Dakich breaks down Kentucky's victory over Arizona State.
videos.headline: Kentucky puts on dominant performance in win over Arizona State
